PrecisReappointment of DALE PARKER, of Vancouver, British Columbia, RICHARD MURRAY THOMSON, of Toronto, Ontario, M. JOSEPH REGAN, of Campbellcroft, Ontario, and DAVID WALKER, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as directors of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period ending October 26, 2004.
